-- =============================================================================
-- FOREX SERVER
-- forexserver
-- v0.8.4-NO-STALE-TRADING
--
-- Purpose:
--   Pull the live EUR/USD number from the Oracle relay node and keep a proper
--   server-side history of candles so clients can boot with an already-built
--   chart instead of starting from a single candle.
--
-- This build:
--   - safe self updater using startup.new/startup.old
--   - polls Oracle /latest every 0.1s
--   - stores persistent 1m and 5m candle history on the server
--   - serves live tick + history to forex clients over rednet
